sentences: Eu Phoria (ユーフォーリア, Yūfōria) was a Japanese all-female band, formed in 2002.
They made their major debut in 2007 on Avex's label Sonic Groove.
The band's final performance was on October 31, 2009.
Shoco and Tomo² joined in 2005, and Sawa² joined a year later.
